lyrics:
Aw, zan thianghlim, mawi takin arsi an eng,
Kan Chhandamtu Krista lo piannaah;
Rei tak khawvel sual leh thimhnuaia leng tawh,
Tunah thlamuanna ropui a thleng ta;
Beiseina tharin khawvel lawmin a khat,
Ni ropui leh lawmawm a eng tan ta,
Chibai bukin, aw, van angel thu ngai r'u,
Aw, zan duhawm, Lal Krista pian hun chu;
Aw, zan thianghlim, aw, zan, aw, zan thianghlim.

Ran in tlawmah Chhandamtu zalna hmun chu,
Thinlung lawmin rinna eng chuan min thlen;
Hruaitu chungtiang siar ropui eng mawi chuan,
Khawchhak mi fingte kawng a rawn hruai a,
Lalberte Lalber chu ranthlengah a zal;
Lungngaih, mangan lai thian rinawm ber chu;
Kan chak lohna lai leh mamawh zawngte a hria,
Chibai bukin Lalber chu chawimawi r'u,
Chibai bukin Lalber chu chawimawi r'u.

Inhmangaih tawn turin min zirtir thin kha
A thupek chu hmangaihna leh remna;
Sual phuarte leh riangvaite chhan chhuak zelin,
A hmingin sual hnehchhiahnate a bo;
A hming thianghlim leh ropui ta chu fakin,
Lawmna hla mawi chu kan sa rual ang a;
Lal Krista chu chatuana Lalber a ni,
A thiltihtheih leh a ropuina chu,
Chatuan, chatuan, chatuana zual zel tur.
